(18, 'About us', '<h2 class=\"blue text-center\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 30px; font-size: 30px; font-family: Roboto; color: rgb(11, 68, 149);\">Putting the Client Before the Clock</h2><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 7px 0px 20px; color: rgb(65, 67, 72); font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">We are a U.S.-based immigration law firm where you can get legal advice directly from the managing attorney. Our managing attorney Raju Mahajan, Esq. and the Raju Law team, help each client to reach their dream Green Card all over the U.S. and get immigration-related services. In addition, our knowledge of Bangladesh and South Asia helps us write personalized petitions and recommendation letters for every applicant.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 7px 0px 20px; color: rgb(65, 67, 72); font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">About us, as knowledgeable, dedicated, and compassionate, The Law Office of Attorney Raju Mahajan, Esq. work individually with each client to solve their problems and achieve the best possible results. We promise to be upfront about your options and the possible outcomes, providing you with the information needed to make informed decisions. We will also help you navigate the often complicated and confusing legal processes involving Immigration and Investment.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 7px 0px 20px; color: rgb(65, 67, 72); font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Ours is a technology-based service where you will get most of your work done online, using several software and websites for quality service and time-saving. We try to ensure maximum attorney-client contact and the fastest and safest way to ensure client satisfaction.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 7px 0px 20px; color: rgb(65, 67, 72); font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">We value long-term relationships with our clients more than money. We provide more affordable financial plans and pricing than almost every other law firm in the country because of our experience in the economic hardships of immigrants and students. We were in your shoes just a few years ago. We know how hard immigrants’ lives are in America.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 7px 0px 20px; color: rgb(65, 67, 72); font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">The Team of Raju Law is always ready to help you reach your dream destination.</p><h2 class=\"blue text-center pt-5\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 30px; font-size: 30px; font-family: Roboto; color: rgb(11, 68, 149);\">Why Choose Us?</h2><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 7px 0px 20px; color: rgb(65, 67, 72); font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">We are one of the fastest growing law firms that provide legal advice directly from the managing attorney, ensuring the best possible outcome.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 7px 0px 20px; color: rgb(65, 67, 72); font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">We conduct rigorous legal research on our clients’ specific study areas in Westlaw and LexisNexis to connect every case with valid and solid legal references. We also use classified data from Data.Gov and Welch Consulting to strengthen the connection between clients’ research and U.S. National Interest. Furthermore, to make our clients’ petition more persuasive, we include a short paragraph on clients’ social and cultural backgrounds that makes our approach unique compared to the corporate law firms.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 7px 0px 20px; color: rgb(6