(15, 6, 'Helen H. Partlow, Esq.', 'Supervising Attorney', 'files/3F2G7Szh0AAyuLxCK77SlSjnylwPK25jjI4ZhPUB.png', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18.75pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Roboto;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\ncolor:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\n#404040;mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:text1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:\n100.0%;mso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Helen Partlow is an attorney with over\n10 years of experience. She is working as an Supervising Attorney at our\norganization. With a passion for helping individuals and families navigate the\ncomplexities of the immigration system, Helen Partlow has built a reputation\nfor providing expert guidance and unwavering support to her clients.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18.75pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Roboto;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\ncolor:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\n#404040;mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:text1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:\n100.0%;mso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Helen holds a Juris Doctor degree from\nthe Touro University Jacob D. Fuchsberg Law Center and a Bachelor’s degree in\nHistory from St. Joseph’s College.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18.75pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Roboto;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\ncolor:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\n#404040;mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:text1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:\n100.0%;mso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">All through her professional life,\nHelen Partlow has successfully represented clients in a variety of matters,\nincluding national interest waivers and responses to requests for evidence. She\nis well-versed in the latest immigration laws and regulations and has a deep\nunderstanding of the challenges that her clients face.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18.75pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Roboto;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\ncolor:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\n#404040;mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:text1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:\n100.0%;mso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">She is committed to making a positive\nimpact in the lives of those she serves and is dedicated to helping her clients\nachieve their immigration goals.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:19.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#01476A;letter-spacing:-.3pt;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\"><br>\n</span><b><span style=\"font-size:19.0pt;\nfont-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;color:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\n#404040;mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:text1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:\n100.0%;mso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;\nletter-spacing:-.3pt;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Education<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 18.75pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#404040;\nmso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#404040;\nmso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:text1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%;\nmso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: