sion Against Discrimination (MCAD). She was a\ncrucial cog in the wheel, helping people from all walks of life build strong\ndiscrimination cases. Stacey was instrumental in planning three highly attended\nconferences on reproductive rights, international human rights, and implicit\nbias and microaggressions while serving as the Black Law Students Society’s\nSecretary.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18.75pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Roboto;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\ncolor:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\n#404040;mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:text1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:\n100.0%;mso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Stacey holds a Bachelor’s degree in\nCriminal Justice from Stockton University and a Master of Science in\nCriminology from Arizona State University. Her experience in law enforcement,\ncommunity outreach, and civil rights work makes her an asset to the Rajulaw\nteam.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18.75pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Roboto;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\ncolor:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\n#404040;mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:text1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:\n100.0%;mso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Stacey is dedicated to acting with the\nutmost integrity and professionalism, and she has honed her excellent communication\nskills by interacting with a wide variety of people in her field. These people\ninclude administrators, court staff, police officers, parole officers, social\nworkers, and families.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18.75pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Roboto;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\ncolor:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\n#404040;mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:text1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:\n100.0%;mso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">At Rajulaw, Stacey leverages her\nunique experiences and skillset to provide top-notch support to clients\nnavigating the immigration process.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:19.0pt;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:\n191;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#404040;mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor:\ntext1;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%;mso-style-textfill-fill-colortransforms:\n&quot;lumm=75000 lumo=25000&quot;;letter-spacing:-.3pt;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatu